105
00:06:53,097 --> 00:06:56,197
But there are other things that bother me about her.

106
00:06:56,197 --> 00:06:58,397
-Ron! -Ron?

107
00:06:58,597 --> 00:07:02,997
Sorry. I'm playing mahjong with the neighbors.

108
00:07:02,997 --> 00:07:04,403
Well, that's the story.

109
00:07:04,403 --> 00:07:06,097
So, if you want to find the culprit,

110
00:07:06,097 --> 00:07:09,297
I suggest you go looking elsewhere.

111
00:07:09,297 --> 00:07:11,197
What did Dad say?

112
00:07:11,197 --> 00:07:15,097
He says he's busy playing mahjong, so to go look somewhere else.

113
