159
00:09:20,539 --> 00:09:22,097
Go and look into that.

160
00:09:22,097 --> 00:09:23,597
Yes, sir!

161
00:09:25,197 --> 00:09:27,197
-Yuko. -Yeah?

162
00:09:27,197 --> 00:09:31,597
May I speak to you in the living room for a moment?

163
00:09:31,597 --> 00:09:33,397
Sure.

164
00:09:36,797 --> 00:09:40,559
So? What's it about?

165
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:43,397
Article 42, sub-paragraph 01 of the penal code...

166
00:09:43,397 --> 00:09:44,563
What?

167
00:09:44,563 --> 00:09:45,797
Criminal offenders who turn themselves in

168
00:09:45,797 --> 00:09:49,397
